      <description><![CDATA[ <h3>ParkShelf 1.0.4</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> live window previews now appear correctly in the <strong>Liquid Glass</strong> and <strong>Liquid Glass Clear</strong> appearances (they were hidden in 1.0.3).</li>
  <li><strong>Auto-doze:</strong> the shelf collapses to its compact puck after a few seconds idle even when pinned &mdash; pinning now only locks the shelf's position.</li>
  <li><strong>Appearances:</strong> choose <strong>Liquid Glass</strong> or <strong>Liquid Glass Clear</strong> with <strong>Translucency</strong> and <strong>Tint</strong> sliders to fine-tune the glass (Settings &rarr; ParkShelf).</li>
</ul> ]]></description>
